    "title": "Mamaearth is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Mamaearth! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Jabalpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Mamaearth:\nMamaearth is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mamaearth!",
